    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## [Intake] CAIAC Lead Capture v2.0.0\n\nCAIAC's own inbound lead capture from web forms (Typeform shape).\nReplaces: CAIAC Demo - Lead Capture v1.2.0\n\n**Trigger:** POST /intake/caiac/lead?slug=caiac\n**Auth:** Add Header Auth credential to webhook node (x-caiac-key)\n**Dedup key:** intake_fingerprint = deterministic hash of email\n**DB gate:** caiac.leads INSERT happens before Sheet write\n**PII boundary:** name/email/phone in Sheet only — never in caiac.leads\n**AI scoring:** delegated to [Utility] Score Lead v1.0.0 (qualification score only)\n\nRequires Step 0 migration + caiac self-client row to be seeded.",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 520,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "note",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-208, -320]
    },
